#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.78"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.78:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Yodhājīvavagga "
msgstr "8. Warriors "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Dutiyaanāgatabhayasutta "
msgstr "78. Future Perils (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.103, sc1
msgctxt "an5.78:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, anāgatabhayāni sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, seeing these five future perils is quite enough for a wilderness mendicant to meditate diligently, keenly, and resolutely for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.78:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "An offending mendicant reflects: "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.4"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho etarahi daharo yuvā susukāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena samannāgato paṭhamena vayasā. "
msgstr "‘Currently I’m a youth, young, black-haired, blessed with youth, in the prime of life. "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.5"
msgid "Hoti kho pana so samayo yaṃ imaṃ kāyaṃ jarā phusati. "
msgstr "But there will come a time when this body is struck with old age. "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.6"
msgid "Jiṇṇena kho pana jarāya abhibhūtena na sukaraṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ manasi kātuṃ, na sukarāni araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevituṃ. "
msgstr "When you’re old, overcome by old age, it’s not easy to focus on the instructions of the Buddhas, and it’s not easy to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.7"
msgid "Purā maṃ so dhammo āgacchati aniṭṭho akanto amanāpo; "
msgstr "Before that unlikable, undesirable, and disagreeable thing happens, "

#. VAR: paṭikacceva → paṭigacceva (bj)
#. VAR: phāsuṃ → phāsu (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.78:1.8"
msgid "handāhaṃ paṭikacceva vīriyaṃ ārabhāmi appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, yenāhaṃ dhammena samannāgato jiṇṇakopi phāsuṃ viharissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "I’d better preempt it by rousing up energy for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. That way, when it happens, I’ll live comfortably even though I’m old.’ "

msgctxt "an5.78:1.9"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "This is the first future peril … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.104, sc2
msgctxt "an5.78:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a wilderness mendicant reflects: "

msgctxt "an5.78:2.2"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho etarahi appābādho appātaṅko samavepākiniyā gahaṇiyā samannāgato nātisītāya nāccuṇhāya majjhimāya padhānakkhamāya. "
msgstr "‘Currently, I’m rarely ill or unwell. My stomach digests well, being neither too hot nor too cold, but just right, and fit for meditation. "

msgctxt "an5.78:2.3"
msgid "Hoti kho pana so samayo yaṃ imaṃ kāyaṃ byādhi phusati. "
msgstr "But there will come a time when this body is struck with sickness. "

#. VAR: byādhinā abhibhūtena → byādhābhibhūtena (bj, mr) | vyādhābhibhūtena (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.78:2.4"
msgid "Byādhitena kho pana byādhinā abhibhūtena na sukaraṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ manasi kātuṃ, na sukarāni araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevituṃ. "
msgstr "When you’re sick, overcome by sickness, it’s not easy to focus on the instructions of the Buddhas, and it’s not easy to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an5.78:2.5"
msgid "Purā maṃ so dhammo āgacchati aniṭṭho akanto amanāpo; "
msgstr "Before that unlikable, undesirable, and disagreeable thing happens, "

msgctxt "an5.78:2.6"
msgid "handāhaṃ paṭikacceva vīriyaṃ ārabhāmi appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, yenāhaṃ dhammena samannāgato byādhitopi phāsuṃ viharissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "I’d better preempt it by rousing up energy for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. That way, when it happens, I’ll live comfortably even though I’m sick.’ "

msgctxt "an5.78:2.7"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "This is the second future peril … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.78:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a wilderness mendicant reflects: "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.2"
msgid "‘etarahi kho subhikkhaṃ susassaṃ sulabhapiṇḍaṃ, sukaraṃ uñchena paggahena yāpetuṃ. "
msgstr "‘Currently, there’s plenty of food, a good harvest, so it’s easy to get alms-food, and easy to keep going by collecting alms. "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.3"
msgid "Hoti kho pana so samayo yaṃ dubbhikkhaṃ hoti dussassaṃ dullabhapiṇḍaṃ, na sukaraṃ uñchena paggahena yāpetuṃ. "
msgstr "But there will come a time of famine, a bad harvest, when it’s hard to get alms-food, and not easy to keep going by collecting alms. "

#. VAR: tena saṅkamanti → tenupasaṅkamanti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.78:3.4"
msgid "Dubbhikkhe kho pana manussā yena subhikkhaṃ tena saṅkamanti. "
msgstr "In a time of famine, people move to where there’s plenty of food, "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.5"
msgid "Tattha saṅgaṇikavihāro hoti ākiṇṇavihāro. "
msgstr "where they live crowded and cramped together. "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.6"
msgid "Saṅgaṇikavihāre kho pana sati ākiṇṇavihāre na sukaraṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ manasi kātuṃ, na sukarāni araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevituṃ. "
msgstr "When you live crowded and cramped together, it’s not easy to focus on the instructions of the Buddhas, and it’s not easy to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.7"
msgid "Purā maṃ so dhammo āgacchati aniṭṭho akanto amanāpo; "
msgstr "Before that unlikable, undesirable, and disagreeable thing happens, "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.8"
msgid "handāhaṃ paṭikacceva vīriyaṃ ārabhāmi appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, yenāhaṃ dhammena samannāgato dubbhikkhepi phāsu viharissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "I’d better preempt it by rousing up energy for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. That way, when it happens, I’ll live comfortably even though there’s a famine.’ "

msgctxt "an5.78:3.9"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "This is the third future peril … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.105, sc4
msgctxt "an5.78:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a wilderness mendicant reflects: "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.2"
msgid "‘etarahi kho manussā samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti. "
msgstr "‘Currently, people live in harmony, appreciating each other, without quarreling, blending like milk and water, and regarding each other with kindly eyes. "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.3"
msgid "Hoti kho pana so samayo yaṃ bhayaṃ hoti aṭavisaṅkopo, cakkasamārūḷhā jānapadā pariyāyanti. "
msgstr "But there will come a time of peril from wild savages, when the countryfolk mount their vehicles and flee everywhere. "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.4"
msgid "Bhaye kho pana sati manussā yena khemaṃ tena saṅkamanti. "
msgstr "In a time of peril, people move to where there’s sanctuary, "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.5"
msgid "Tattha saṅgaṇikavihāro hoti ākiṇṇavihāro. "
msgstr "where they live crowded and cramped together. "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.6"
msgid "Saṅgaṇikavihāre kho pana sati ākiṇṇavihāre na sukaraṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ manasi kātuṃ, na sukarāni araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevituṃ. "
msgstr "When you live crowded and cramped together, it’s not easy to focus on the instructions of the Buddhas, and it’s not easy to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.7"
msgid "Purā maṃ so dhammo āgacchati aniṭṭho akanto amanāpo; "
msgstr "Before that unlikable, undesirable, and disagreeable thing happens, "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.8"
msgid "handāhaṃ paṭikacceva vīriyaṃ ārabhāmi appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, yenāhaṃ dhammena samannāgato bhayepi phāsuṃ viharissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "I’d better preempt it by rousing up energy for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. That way, when it happens, I’ll live comfortably even in a time of peril.’ "

msgctxt "an5.78:4.9"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, catutthaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "This is the fourth future peril … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an5.78:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, a wilderness mendicant reflects: "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.2"
msgid "‘etarahi kho saṅgho samaggo sammodamāno avivadamāno ekuddeso phāsu viharati. "
msgstr "‘Currently, the Saṅgha lives comfortably, in harmony, appreciating each other, without quarreling, with one recitation. "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.3"
msgid "Hoti kho pana so samayo yaṃ saṅgho bhijjati. "
msgstr "But there will come a time of schism in the Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.4"
msgid "Saṅghe kho pana bhinne na sukaraṃ buddhānaṃ sāsanaṃ manasi kātuṃ, na sukarāni araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevituṃ. "
msgstr "When there is schism in the Saṅgha, it’s not easy to focus on the instructions of the Buddhas, and it’s not easy to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.5"
msgid "Purā maṃ so dhammo āgacchati aniṭṭho akanto amanāpo; "
msgstr "Before that unlikable, undesirable, and disagreeable thing happens, "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.6"
msgid "handāhaṃ paṭikacceva vīriyaṃ ārabhāmi appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, yenāhaṃ dhammena samannāgato bhinnepi saṅghe phāsuṃ viharissāmī’ti. "
msgstr "I’d better preempt it by rousing up energy for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized. That way, when it happens, I’ll live comfortably even though there’s schism in the Saṅgha.’ "

msgctxt "an5.78:5.7"
msgid "Idaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamaṃ anāgatabhayaṃ sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
msgstr "This is the fifth future peril … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an5.78:6.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca anāgatabhayāni sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā appamattena ātāpinā pahitattena viharituṃ appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five future perils, seeing which is quite enough for a wilderness mendicant to meditate diligently, keenly, and resolutely for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.78:6.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

